      <title>英国央行和市场对 6 月份降息前景看法一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/boe-and-markets-fall-into-line-over-prospect-of-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，英国央行和市场在利率方向上一直存在争执——美联储在塑造预期方面比英国央行的言论更有力量——他们现在已经大致整齐划一了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/boe-and-markets-fall-into-line-over-prospect-of-june-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 17:07:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
